  "authors": [],
  "body": {
    "comment": "I am changing my ABSTAIN vote to YES for the proposal 'Net Change Limit of 300 Million ADA for Epochs 613–713' (gov_action1wwjwkg2g0qwr0mehey9r8gwn6qz3r28wl6wdl2s75kfmpy8j87tqqtft9tp). While I stand by my previous rationale regarding governance action proposal quality, the vote here at the expiration time of this Info Action is almost too close to call. There has remained some uncertainty among certain community members over whether or not the previous NCL passed or did not pass as a result of a lack of Constitutional Committee participation (1 vote shy of “typical” threshold). This proposal currently has 6/7 Constitutional Committee votes. The Cardano ecosystem has dealt with far too much negativity and animosity of late and so I submit this vote in the hope of getting this proposal over the line and put an end to any potential uncertainty so that this ecosystem can move on without getting embroiled in yet more public drama."
  },
  "hashAlgorithm": "blake2b-256"
}
